descriptionNullable: This dataset consists of a total of 4,000 images (2,000 real & 2,000 fake). Real images are taken from the CIFAKE dataset's real images (32x32) . Fake images were generated using Midjourney v6. There are 10 classes (airplane, car, bird, cat, deer, frog, horse, ship, truck).
